.Bl -tag -width "xxx" -offset indent
.It Li db-dir = Va path
This parameter defines a directory that can contain:
.Bl -tag -width "xxx" -offset indent
.It Va kdc.conf
A configuration file with the same format as krb5.conf that will
be included.
.It Va m-key
